long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
SaveMyTabs Manager can be used to save URLs from any website. Build a list of targeted leads to keep track of. You can enter a URL or any website and click the 'Save Input' button, or just visit any URL that is in your current tab and save it by clicking on the ‘Save Tab’ button.

What you can do with this app:

Fetch and save URLs from any site.
100% of the URLs are saved on the URL Saver.

Updated: August 7th, 2024 - Version v0.0.0.7 2024
User will be able to add, edit, and delete folders one by one
User will be able to add, save custom, edit, delete any URL and delete all URLs.
User will be able to edit the title of any URL.

Subscription Features
- Add more folders
- Search saved URLS

Want better features? Subscribe now to add more than one folder and search through your saved URLs. Unlock the full potential of SaveMyTabs Manager!

Upcoming Subscription Features.
- Delete all folders
- Copy a link
- Download Links as Text Document, PDF, Word Document, CSV file
- Save Folder with links as a bookmark
